#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-extractrc.1.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "Extract message strings from UI and GUI-RC files"
msgstr ""
"Udtræk meddelelsestrenge fra UI og RC-filer for den grafiske grænseflade"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-extractrc.1.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>extractrc</command> <group><option><replaceable>filename</"
"replaceable></option></group>"
msgstr ""
"<command>extractrc</command> <group><option><replaceable>filnavn</"
"replaceable></option></group>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-extractrc.1.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Beskrivelse"

#. Tag: para
#: man-extractrc.1.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>extractrc</command> finds all text tags and other message strings "
"in the given files and writes the corresponding i18n() calls to standard "
"output so that xgettext can parse them."
msgstr ""
"<command>extractrc</command> finder alle tekstmærker og andre "
"meddelelsestrenge i givne filer og skriver tilsvarende i18n()-kald til "
"standardudskriften så xgettext kan tolke dem."

#. Tag: para
#: man-extractrc.1.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It understands both (&Qt;/&kde;) <application>designer</application>'s "
"<acronym>UI</acronym> files and &XML; GUI-RC files."
msgstr ""
"Det forstår både (&Qt;/&kde;) <application>Designer</application> "
"<acronym>UI</acronym>-filer og &XML; RC-filer."

#. Tag: para
#: man-extractrc.1.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "This utility is part of the KDE Software Development Kit."
msgstr "Værktøjet er en del af KDE's programmeludviklingsmiljø."

